108
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:05,680
Honestly, it's hard to explain.

109
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:08,320
Are you leaving or not?

110
00:05:08,510 --> 00:05:09,470
No.

111
00:05:10,820 --> 00:05:12,260
I just became

112
00:05:12,460 --> 00:05:13,510
the gang leader again.

113
00:05:14,060 --> 00:05:15,700
I won't give it up that easily.

114
00:05:16,260 --> 00:05:17,960
But it was never about the title.

115
00:05:18,190 --> 00:05:19,510
Otherwise, you wouldn't have

116
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:20,560
given it to my dad.

117
00:05:20,990 --> 00:05:21,870
You just wanted to

118
00:05:21,870 --> 00:05:23,240
take on the responsibility yourself

119
00:05:23,430 --> 00:05:24,510
