191
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:00,040
Anyway,

192
00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:01,390
son,

193
00:08:01,390 --> 00:08:02,840
listen to me.

194
00:08:03,830 --> 00:08:05,300
Don't trust Cheng Hui.

195
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:06,550
He's

196
00:08:07,390 --> 00:08:08,360
always

197
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:10,360
